               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i0">
                     <locus from="1v" to="15v">1v-15v</locus>
                     <textLang xml:lang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
                     <title type="lacunous" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT0049IHA#s17IHA">قران, Tenth ǧuz’ (10/30)</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#1v">-1v</locus>وَاعْلَمٌوا أَنَّمَا غَنِمْتُمْ مِّنْ شَيْ فَأَنَّ لِلهِ خُمُسَهُ وَلِلرَّسُولِ ولِذِي القُرْبَي وَاليَتَمي وَالمَسَكِينَ وَابْنِ السَّبِيلِ</incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="ar">
                        <locus target="#15r">-15r</locus>وَطَبَعَ اللهُ عَلَي قُلُبِهِم فَهُمْ لَا يَعْلَموُنَ </explicit>
                     <note>8:41-9:93. Elegant, and professional hand. Regular ihmāl signs on kāfs, which are almost without final stroke on the top. 12 lines a page. Rubricated title of suras. Several words completed in the following line. Words, which were started on a line, were entirely rewritten the following line in a lot of places. Some words completed in the margins with a space left to respect the margin line on the left. Deletions, and corrections after revision. Catchwords. Few margins, ǧuz’ and ḥizb mark in red (1v; 8r). Manuscript disorganized (loose folios) and lacunous (1v/2r).</note>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
